00:02:08.889 --> 00:02:15.800
and breathing in, breathing out.

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.075
And one more time--

00:02:17.075 --> 00:02:21.650
breathing in and breathing out.

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.895
Now we're here just
